descriptionHtml:
Tiv is the best rewards platform for Xbox, Steam & Playstation gamers. Earn points by playing games on any of 3 platforms!

Redeem your points for gift cards or cash. You choose!
Boost the points you earn by signing up for an optional Tiv VISA Debit Card.

No credit check. No annual fee. FDIC Insured.*

Complete gaming quests to earn points and multiply the value of those points up to 5x when you spend on your Tiv card. No rotating spend categories to keep track of. Earn maximum rewards spending how you want!

HOW IT WORKS

Connect your gaming accounts and rake in points every time you complete a quest! Tiv quests let you earn points for playing any game you want.

Earn bonus points by completing one-off featured quests! Team up with fellow gamers or drop in solo - your choice!

Finally the gamers black card has arrived! Every $100 you spend with your Tiv card multiplies the value of your points up to 5x! The debit card with credit card-like rewards - ONLY for gamers.

Redeem your points for cash at any time as a Tiv card member. No out of stock gift cards, no hoops to jump through. Your points from gaming today can pay for groceries or the latest DLC tomorrow - you choose!

Withdraw your money at any time and rest easy knowing it is fully FDIC insured - there’s no risk.

Start using your account right away when you activate your virtual debit card.

100% FREE

No annual fees, no credit check. Play what you want, pay where you want and redeem when you want. It’s that simple.

IS TIV SECURE?

• Your account is FDIC insured and held at Blue Ridge Bank. FDIC insurance means your cash is fully guaranteed by the U.S government for up to $250,000.

• We protect the privacy of your information and will never share your data with any third party without your permission.

• We use bank-level encryption and no sensitive information is ever stored on our servers.
